# 🚀 Day 84/90 – AI Explanation Section

Congratulations! 🎉

Today you'll add an **AI Explanation** section to the report.

⚠️ **Important:** We're **not connecting to OpenAI yet**. Instead, we'll simulate the AI by displaying a smart explanation based on the hemoglobin value.

Later, when we deploy to AWS, we'll replace this logic with real OpenAI API calls.

---

# 🎯 Goal

Your report screen will now contain:

```text
Patient Information
-------------------

Health Interpretation
-------------------

🤖 AI Explanation
-------------------

Your hemoglobin value appears to be within the normal range.
Maintain a balanced diet and continue regular health checkups.
```

or

```text
🤖 AI Explanation

Your hemoglobin level is lower than normal.
This may indicate iron deficiency or anemia.
Please consult your doctor for further evaluation.
```

